{"tid":2123581,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子在美國駐成都總領館外放鞭炮被帶走","createTime":"2020-07-24T17:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T22:47:49.000Z","uid":360777,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b0ced0fa36d78fa305caf55b5245a1ac0ecdbf","tid":2123581,"uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T17:59:24.000Z","msg":"中國外交部通知美方關閉美國駐成都總領事館，反制美國要求中方關閉駐休斯敦總領事館。成都警方通報，<strong>昨天晚上7時許，一男子步行至領事館路時，從隨身攜帶的袋中取出一串鞭炮點燃，民警迅速將他帶離。鞭炮燃放未造成現場人員受傷。</strong><br />\n<br />\n警方說，公安機關已依法對這名男子作出行政警告處罰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539761-20200725.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539761-20200725.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=60170dba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539761-20200725.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f6e9654e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539761-20200725.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e96dc51c8331f64b8c379d2e9ed4acc7c5ea609a","tid":2123581,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T21:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d309d843ef309af66a93ede398a2f2c47ce5a218","tid":2123581,"uid":173271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T22:42:21.000Z","msg":"識玩梗係拍膊頭帶走啦<br />\n同元朗白衣一樣"},{"pid":"2d64ecdfc804e9748f718463073c5654aac62edf","tid":2123581,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T22:45:28.000Z","msg":"原來會錯意<br />\n唔是包圍美國領事館<br />\n係保護美國領事館<br />\nd小粉紅花咁多時間睇中國保護美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4f006324cb16bb9547c55decfaf41b165aae8c","tid":2123581,"uid":136735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T22:47:29